    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ev_rules",
      "x": 810,
      "y": 765,
      "width": 375,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "• Balance deducted only on APPROVE (reject = no impact)\n• >3 days leave → multi-level approval (+ HR)\n• Conflict detection: warning if dates overlap\n• Amendment TS = separate approval workflow\n• Manager can delegate approval (MGR-11)\n• Mobile function mirrors all web features (MGR-12)\n• WFS data integrates to Payroll on schedule\n• Authentication via SF SSO (single sign-on)",
      "originalText": "• Balance deducted only on APPROVE (reject = no impact)\n• >3 days leave → multi-level approval (+ HR)\n• Conflict detection: warning if dates overlap\n• Amendment TS = separate approval workflow\n• Manager can delegate approval (MGR-11)\n• Mobile function mirrors all web features (MGR-12)\n• WFS data integrates to Payroll on schedule\n• Authentication via SF SSO (single sign-on)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
